Any organisation which needs to build a Devops platform for multitenancy using Kubernetes might need to involve the below building blocks :

1. Multi-Tenant Onboarding to Cluster
2. CNI support for Multi-Tenant Networking
3. Control Plane and Multi-Tenant Compute Plane isolation.
4. RBAC
5. Multi-Tenant Access to Cluster
6. Multi-Tenant Logging(Fluentd) and Monitoring(Prometheus)
7. Kubernetes Cluster upgrade and impact to Multi-Tenant Workloads
8. Multi-Tenant Image Isolation
9. Securing the Multi-Tenant Container(Container Immutability)
10. Building the CICD Pipelines and Image repository for Multi-tenancy.
11. Multi-tenant Container Image on-boarding.

